<h1>Your Referral Payout Account</h1>

<p>
  Your MOSSLET account has been deleted as requested, but we wanted to make sure you know about your Stripe Express payout account.
</p>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="info">
  <strong>üí∞ Your Stripe Account Is Still Active</strong>
  <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
    Your Stripe Express account (where referral payouts are sent) remains active and is completely separate from your MOSSLET account.
  </p>
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<%= if @available_payout > 0 do %>
  <EmailComponents.status type="success">
    <strong>‚úÖ Final Payout Processed</strong>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
      We transferred <strong>{@available_payout_formatted}</strong>
      to your Stripe account before deletion.
    </p>
  </EmailComponents.status>
  <EmailComponents.gap />
<% end %>

<%= if @pending_amount > 0 do %>
  <EmailComponents.status type="warning">
    <strong>‚è≥ Pending Earnings: {@pending_amount_formatted}</strong>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
      You have earnings still in the waiting period (protection against chargebacks). These will automatically be transferred to your Stripe account when they clear ‚Äî no action needed from you.
    </p>
  </EmailComponents.status>
  <EmailComponents.gap />
<% end %>

<h2>How to Access Your Stripe Account</h2>

<p>
  You can manage your Stripe Express account, view your balance, update your bank details, or close it directly through Stripe:
</p>

<EmailComponents.button_centered
  to="https://connect.stripe.com/express_login"
  color="blue"
  size="lg"
>
  Go to Stripe Express Dashboard
</EmailComponents.button_centered>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>
  When you visit the link above, Stripe will send a login link to your email address (<strong>{@email}</strong>).
</p>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.top_border>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    <strong>What you can do in your Stripe dashboard:</strong>
    <ul style="margin-top: 8px;">
      <li>View your current balance and payout history</li>
      <li>Update your bank account or debit card for payouts</li>
      <li>Download tax documents (1099 forms)</li>
      <li>Close your Stripe account when you're ready</li>
    </ul>
  </EmailComponents.small_text>

  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@mosslet.com">support@mosslet.com</a>.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
</EmailComponents.top_border>
